msgid "santussito nāma devaputto … "
msgstr "the god named Santussita … "

#. REF: pts-cs76
msgctxt "dn11:76.1"
msgid "nimmānaratī nāma devā … "
msgstr "the gods who delight in creation … "

#. REF: pts-cs77
msgctxt "dn11:77.1"
msgid "sunimmito nāma devaputto … "
msgstr "the god named Sunimmita … "

msgctxt "dn11:77.2"
msgid "paranimmitavasavattī nāma devā … "
msgstr "the gods who control the creation of others … "

#. REF: pts-cs78
msgctxt "dn11:78.1"
msgid "vasavattī nāma devaputto amhehi abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro ca. "
